\v 76
\v 1 Mwari anozikanwa pakati paJudha;
\s Zita rake iguru pakati palsiraeri.
\p
\v 2 PaSaremiwo ndipo pane
\s tabhenakeri yake,
\s NapaZioni ugaro hwake.
\p
\v 3 Ndipo paakavhuna miseve youta;
\s Nenhoo, nomunondo, nokurwa.
\p
\v 4 Imi munokubwinya, makanaka kwazvo,
\s Kupfuura makomo ezvakapambwa.
\p
\v 5 Vakatsunga pamwoyo,
\s vakapambwa,
\s vakavata hope dzavo;
\s Pakati pavarume vane simba hakuna akawana
\s maoko ake.
\p
\v 6 Pakutuka kwenyu, Mwari waJakobho,
\s Ngoro nebhiza zvose zvinobatwa nehope dzorufu.
